7:
The region of Gilead is mine;\q1 the people of the tribe of Manasseh are mine;
\q1 the tribe of Ephraim is like my helmet;
\q1 and the tribe of Judah is like the scepter with which I rule.


\q1

8:
The region of Moab is like my washbasin;\q2 I throw my sandal into the region of Edom to show that it belongs to me;
\q2 I shout triumphantly because I have defeated the people of all the region of Philistia.
\q1
